Package model

Provides all classes for the controller component.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IModel
    The Interface IModel.
    IMonster  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoneH
    BoneH is the class defining horizontal bones objects.
    BoneS
    BoneS is the class defining corner bones objects.
    BoneV
    BoneV is the class defining vertical bones objects.
    CrystalBall
    CrystalBall is the class defining CrystallBall image.
    Door_out
    Door_out is the class defining door's display according to his state.
    Fire_Ball
    Fire_Ball is the class defining fireball's color according to his movement.
    Game_BOOT
    Game management, sprite display and loading elements
    Lorann_Mobile
    Lorann_Mobile is the class defining Lorann's display according to his movement.
    Map
    The Class Map.
    Mobile_Elements
    Mobile Elements is the class inherited by the moving objects of the game such as Lorann and the fireball.
    ModelFacade
    The Class ModelFacade provides a facade of the Model component.
    Monster_1
    Monster_1 is the class defining the 1st monster.
    Monster_2
    Monster_2 is the class defining the 2nd monster.
    Monster_3
    Monster_3 is the class defining the 3th monster.
    Monster_4
    Monster_4 is the class defining the 4th monster.
    Purse
    Purse is the class defining purses objects.
    Uncrossable
    Uncrossable is a class that manages the HitBox of the objects which will be recovered.
    Walls
    Walls is a class that manages the hitbox of objects that can not be crossed.
